OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,8,F"revealed the full depth of the chasm
OL,9,Fbetween people and Westminster
OL,10,Fpolitics", Andy Burnham has said in
OL,11,Fone of his first public comments on
OL,12,Fthe ballot.
OL,14,FThe Labour mayor of Greater
OL,15,FManchester, who was snubbed by the
OL,16,FLabour Party's ruling body as its
OL,17,Fcandidate for the seat, suggested the
OL,18,Fby-election demonstrated Westminster
OL,19,Fwas not focused on the priorities of
OL,20,Fordinary people.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe Green Party's candidate Hannah
OL,8,FSpencer won the constituency `
OL,9,Fpreviously a Labour stronghold ` in
OL,10,Flast Thursday's by-election.
OL,12,FLabour came third, after Reform UK in
OL,13,Fsecond.
OL,15,FMr Burnham addressed the by-election
OL,16,Fas he appeared at an event hosted by
OL,17,Fthe Centre for Cities think tank in
OL,18,Fcentral London.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FHe told the audience: "From my point
OL,8,Fof view, I'm definitely not here to
OL,9,Ftalk about my career plans, other than
OL,10,Fto say I wrote a book as you might
OL,11,Fknow, with the mayor of the Liverpool
OL,12,FCity region Steve Rotheram, about
OL,13,Fleaving Westminster and establishing
OL,14,Fdevolution across England.
OL,16,F"It's called Head North. All I can say
OL,17,Ftoday is that the sequel Head South is
OL,18,Fcurrently on hold."
OL,26,@oD@WOUxD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FHe added: "What I want to say today is
OL,8,Fthat the time has most definitely come
OL,9,Ffor a serious conversation about our
OL,10,Fpolitical system and its pervading
OL,11,Fculture, particularly so in the
OL,12,Faftermath of the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,13,Felection.
OL,15,F"It revealed the full depth of the
OL,16,Fchasm between people and Westminster
OL,17,Fpolitics. I don't think anybody can
OL,18,Fseriously dispute that statement."
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FMr Burnham described polling by More
OL,8,Fin Common which found a majority of
OL,9,Fpeople do not think the cost-of-living
OL,10,Fcrisis will ever end as "code red for
OL,11,FWestminster politics".
OL,13,FHe added: "This is getting extremely
OL,14,Fdangerous, and change in our political
OL,15,Fsystem and culture is desperately
OL,16,Fneeded."
OL,18,FMr Burnham was asked by reporters why
OL,19,Fhe had considered a return to
OL,20,FWestminster giving his misgivings
OL,21,Fabout the place.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@UO]uD@KOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FHe replied: "I don't think Greater
OL,8,FManchester's full ambitions are
OL,9,Fachievable with the political system
OL,10,Fstaying as it is. There is, in my
OL,11,Fview, a bias against the North of
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,F"I saw it with my own eyes in
OL,15,FWestminster, and not just an emotional
OL,16,Fbias, it's hardwired, it's in the
OL,17,Fgreen book.
OL,26,@oD@MOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,F"Therefore I just don't think in the
OL,8,Frest of this century it (Manchester)
OL,9,Fwill be everything I believe it can be
OL,10,Fwith that culture still pervading,
OL,11,Fwhere we are always begging for things
OL,12,Fand having to constantly lobby for
OL,13,Feverything."
OL,15,FA further attempt by journalists to
OL,16,Fask Mr Burnham about the outcome of
OL,17,Fthe by-election was shut down by
OL,18,FCentre for Cities chief executive
OL,19,FAndrew Carter, who was chairing the
OL,20,Fevent.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FElsewhere in his speech, Mr Burnham
OL,8,Fcalled for further and more widespread
OL,9,Fdevolution of powers across the UK.
OL,11,FCity regions within Scotland and Wales
OL,12,Fshould be given their own devolved
OL,13,Fpowers and responsibilities, beyond
OL,14,Fthose of the devolved national
OL,15,Fgovernments, he suggested.
OL,17,FHe also hit out at a culture within
OL,18,FWestminster of reluctance to devolve
OL,19,Fpowers which could prove more useful
OL,20,Ffor local leaders to hold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,F"What is the rationale for Westminster
OL,8,Fhanging on to all of the power over
OL,9,Fthose things when clearly they can't
OL,10,Fdo it from where they are?" Mr Burnham
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FHe added: "Honestly, I'm getting to
OL,14,Fthe point where I just refuse to spend
OL,15,Fany more of my working week making the
OL,16,Fcase to Whitehall for more devolved
OL,17,Fpowers, because I spent way too much
OL,18,Ftime of my time doing that.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@[O]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772705111
OL,3,CBurnham warns Gorton by-election
OL,4,Crevealed 'chasm' between politics and
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,F"Why aren't they just looking at the
OL,8,Fevidence, getting behind us and
OL,9,Fgetting on with it? It just makes you
OL,10,Fthink they don't actually want growth
OL,11,Feverywhere."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
